.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage local AI coding tasks backed by a repo-family ledger.

.PP
Minimal flow: add -> start -> advance -> attach/show/list -> rm.
Workflow nodes come from ~/.config/gmc/workflow.yaml or ~/.gmc/workflow.yaml.


